cd backend
python app.py
go Live

github
repo - Estimate-BMI-Using-Gender-Height-Weight-ML


<h1>Estimate BMI Using Gender, Height & Weight (Machine Learning)</h1>

<h2>Project Overview</h2>
<p>
This project estimates Body Mass Index (BMI) using Machine Learning
based on Gender, Height, and Weight.
The system includes a web-based frontend and a Python backend
that performs BMI prediction and analysis.
</p>


<h2>Machine Learning</h2>
<p><b>Dataset:</b> BMI data (CSV & JSON)</p>
<p><b>Model Type:</b> Classification / Regression</p>
<p><b>Features:</b></p>
<p>Gender</p>
<p>Height (cm)</p>
<p>Weight (kg)</p>
<p><b>Output:</b></p>
<p>BMI Value</p>
<p>BMI Category (Underweight, Normal, Overweight, Obese)</p>


<h2>Frontend</h2>
<p>HTML Pages:</p>
<p>Home</p>
<p>BMI Calculator</p>
<p>BMI Analysis</p>
<p>Ideal BMI</p>
<p>CSS for styling</p>
<p>JavaScript for validation and interactivity</p>


<h2>Backend</h2>
<p>Python (Flask-based)</p>
<p>Handles:</p>
<p>Data processing</p>
<p>Model prediction</p>
<p>Result generation</p>


